    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire an example in superlative condition. Maintained to the highest standards, the exterior retains its original showroom luster, while the interior remains entirely unblemished. Every mechanical system has been meticulously vetted to ensure it operates at peak factory specifications. This is an investment-grade vehicle for the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than automotive excellence.",
